General.Name: Palomar Holdings Inc
General.Description: Palomar Holdings, Inc., a specialty insurance company, provides property and casualty insurance to individuals and businesses in the United States. The company offers personal and commercial specialty insurance products, including residential and commercial earthquake; fronting; and inland marine and other property products, such as Inland Marine, Hawaii Hurricane, commercial all risk, excess national property, residential flood, and other miscellaneous property products, as well as assumed reinsurance and crop insurance products. It markets and distributes its products through retail agents, wholesale brokers, program administrators, and carrier partnerships. The company was formerly known as GC Palomar Holdings and changed its name to Palomar Holdings, Inc. The company was incorporated in 2013 and is headquartered in La Jolla, California.
